name: pepeGPT
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
$pepeGPT memecoins will be airdropped to $GPT Stakers on the 25th of April.
CryptoGPT is pioneering layer-2 economics to facilitate the tokenized AI economy. The fundamental mission is to empower the community.

What makes your project unique?
That mission includes delivering unexpected yet meaningful opportunities to the community when possible. Therefore, as an exciting gift for $GPT community, pepeGPT will airdrop a 100% fairlaunch memecoin $pepeGPT to $GPT stakers. Everyone who stakes before Monday 10 am UTC qualifies.

History of your project.
Airdrop: $pepeGPT memecoins will be airdropped to $GPT Stakers on the 25th of April.


What’s next for your project?
 CEX listings.nft develop

What can your token be used for?
gpt meme project
